info.description:
Dump Python packages dependencies
=================================

Requirements
------------

* Python 2.7

Installation
------------

.. code-block::

   $ git clone https://github.com/attakei/packdeps.git
   $ cd packdeps
   $ python setup.py install

Usage
-----

#. Install package to dump
#. Install packdeps
#. Run packdeps command

Example
^^^^^^^

.. code-block::

   $ pip install pyramid
   $ (install packdeps)
   $ packdeps pyramid
